2
00:00:10,008 --> 00:00:13,008
Mpango 1: Mapema Asubuhi - Kujiandaa kwa Mtihani

3
00:00:13,008 --> 00:00:16,074
Habari za asubuhi.

4
00:00:16,097 --> 00:00:19,564
Aa, habari za asubuhi.

5
00:00:19,587 --> 00:00:22,853
Sasa ni saa ngapi?

6
00:00:22,876 --> 00:00:26,310
Saa moja na nusu.

7
00:00:26,333 --> 00:00:28,799
Adui!

8
00:00:28,822 --> 00:00:33,181
Leo kuna mtihani katika somo la kwanza.

9
00:00:33,205 --> 00:00:37,195
Kweli? Hiyo ni habari mbaya.

10
00:00:37,219 --> 00:00:40,209
Haraka!

11
00:00:40,232 --> 00:00:45,750
Ndiyo. Sina wakati wa kupika kifungua kinywa.

12
00:00:45,774 --> 00:00:50,367
Kuna mkate juu ya meza.

13
00:00:50,390 --> 00:00:52,823
Utakula?

14
00:00:52,846 --> 00:00:55,632
Asante.

15
00:00:55,656 --> 00:00:58,369
Nakula.

16
00:00:58,392 --> 00:01:01,726
Unataka kahawa pia?

17
00:01:01,749 --> 00:01:04,825
Nitaipika kwa wewe.

18
00:01:04,849 --> 00:01:11,982
Hapana, sina wakati, maji yatatosha.

19
00:01:12,005 --> 00:01:14,238
Sawa.

20
00:01:14,261 --> 00:01:17,980
Mtihani ni mgumu?

21
00:01:18,004 --> 00:01:23,037
Ndiyo, nafikiri ni mgumu sana.

22
00:01:23,060 --> 00:01:28,527
Jana usiku uliosoma sana?

23
00:01:28,551 --> 00:01:34,122
Ndiyo, niliosoma hadi saa sita usiku kwenye maktaba.

24
00:01:34,146 --> 00:01:37,914
Hiyo ni nzuri sana!

25
00:01:37,937 --> 00:01:41,404
Hakika utafaulu.

26
00:01:41,427 --> 00:01:44,160
Asante.

27
00:01:44,183 --> 00:01:46,816
Nitapigana.

28
00:01:46,839 --> 00:01:50,950
Umekwisha jiandaa?

29
00:01:50,974 --> 00:01:56,007
Nimeweka kila kitu ndani ya mfuko.

30
00:01:56,030 --> 00:02:00,547
Basi, twende sasa?

31
00:02:00,571 --> 00:02:04,004
Ndiyo, twende.

32
00:02:04,027 --> 00:02:11,132
Kiungo cha tovuti ambapo unaweza kukagua tena video ya leo kipo kwenye maelezo na kwenye maoni ya juu. *Tovuti inaweza kuondolewa bila tahadhari.

33
00:02:11,132 --> 00:02:14,132
Mpango 2: Usafiri na Hali ya Hewa

34
00:02:14,132 --> 00:02:18,276
Kila siku joto sana, sivyo?

35
00:02:18,299 --> 00:02:21,933
Ndiyo, kweli.

36
00:02:21,956 --> 00:02:26,901
Leo utakwenda shuleni vipi?

37
00:02:26,924 --> 00:02:30,991
Leo nitaenda kwa basi.

38
00:02:31,014 --> 00:02:35,410
Mimi nitaenda kwa baiskeli.

39
00:02:35,433 --> 00:02:41,138
Basi, twende pamoja hadi kituo cha basi.

40
00:02:41,162 --> 00:02:44,395
Sawa, hivi ndivyo tutakavyofanya.

41
00:02:44,418 --> 00:02:50,485
Unachukua dakika ngapi kwenda shuleni kwa baiskeli?

42
00:02:50,508 --> 00:02:56,208
Kama dakika kumi na tano hivi.

43
00:02:56,231 --> 00:02:58,701
Hiyo ni haraka!

44
00:02:58,725 --> 00:03:02,825
Basi inachukua dakika ishirini.

45
00:03:02,848 --> 00:03:10,614
Lakini siku za mvua, baiskeli ni ngumu, kwa hiyo nitaenda kwa basi.

46
00:03:10,637 --> 00:03:14,510
Aa, ndivyo.

47
00:03:14,534 --> 00:03:20,034
Mimi pia nataka baiskeli mpya.

48
00:03:20,057 --> 00:03:24,894
Wikendi hii twende pamoja kuangalia?

49
00:03:24,918 --> 00:03:27,551
Sawa, hiyo ni wazo zuri.

50
00:03:27,574 --> 00:03:31,143
Duka liko wapi?

51
00:03:31,166 --> 00:03:36,866
Kuna duka kubwa mbele ya kituo cha treni.

52
00:03:36,889 --> 00:03:39,523
Je, ni ghali?

53
00:03:39,546 --> 00:03:44,412
Hapana, nadhani si ghali sana.

54
00:03:44,435 --> 00:03:49,634
Aa, huko ndipo kituo cha basi.

55
00:03:49,658 --> 00:03:56,335
Ndiyo. Sasa mimi nitakwenda kwa baiskeli kutoka hapa.

56
00:03:56,358 --> 00:03:59,149
Sawa.

57
00:03:59,172 --> 00:04:02,446
Hatua kwa tahadhari.

58
00:04:02,470 --> 00:04:04,970
Asante.

59
00:04:04,993 --> 00:04:08,093
Tutaonana baadaye.

60
00:04:08,116 --> 00:04:11,116
Mstari 3: Salamu na Vitu Vilivyusahau

61
