Siwezi kusoma kanji hii katika kitabu hiki.

122
00:08:12,742 --> 00:08:15,621
Iko wapi?

123
00:08:15,644 --> 00:08:18,878
Nionyeshe.

124
00:08:18,901 --> 00:08:23,867
Hii ni sehemu yenye herufi nyekundu.

125
00:08:23,890 --> 00:08:30,804
Aa, hii inasomwa 'toshokan'.

126
00:08:30,828 --> 00:08:34,863
'Toshokan', ndiyo?

127
00:08:34,887 --> 00:08:38,246
Inamaanisha nini?

128
00:08:38,269 --> 00:08:43,027
Ni mahali ambapo kuna vitabu vingi.

129
00:08:43,050 --> 00:08:46,183
Sawa.

130
00:08:46,206 --> 00:08:49,506
Asante.

131
00:08:49,529 --> 00:08:53,763
Huna kamusi?

132
00:08:53,786 --> 00:08:58,978
Ndiyo, siku hii sikuleta.

133
00:08:59,002 --> 00:09:03,572
Nakupigie kamusi yangu?

134
00:09:03,595 --> 00:09:06,662
Unaweza?

135
00:09:06,685 --> 00:09:09,351
Asante.

136
00:09:09,374 --> 00:09:13,731
Ndiyo, karibu.

137
00:09:13,755 --> 00:09:17,752
Unasoma kwa ajili ya mtihani wa kesho?

138
00:09:17,776 --> 00:09:21,809
Ndiyo, ni hivyo.

139
00:09:21,832 --> 00:09:25,616
Kuna mengi ya kukumbuka.

140
00:09:25,639 --> 00:09:31,988
Kuna mitihani ya kanji kila wiki, ni ngumu sana.

141
00:09:32,012 --> 00:09:39,193
Ndiyo. Lakini nimepata polepole kuwa bora.

142
00:09:39,217 --> 00:09:42,567
Hiyo ni nzuri sana!

143
00:09:42,590 --> 00:09:47,770
Ndiyo. Nitakurudishia kamusi baadaye.

144
00:09:47,794 --> 00:09:51,231
Usisumbue.

145
00:09:51,255 --> 00:09:55,122
Unaweza kurudisha wakati wowote.

146
00:09:55,145 --> 00:09:58,145
Mandhari ya 6: Mazungumzo Kuhusu Kazi za Muda

147
00:09:58,145 --> 00:10:03,645
Dars ya leo yote yamekwisha, sivyo?

148
00:10:03,668 --> 00:10:06,377
Umechoka sana.

149
00:10:06,400 --> 00:10:09,767
Nimechoka mno.

150
00:10:09,790 --> 00:10:12,490
Mimi pia.

151
00:10:12,513 --> 00:10:16,213
Sasa unakwenda wapi?

152
00:10:16,236 --> 00:10:20,303
Leo nina kazi ya muda.

153
00:10:20,326 --> 00:10:22,826
Ndiyo hivyo.

154
00:10:22,848 --> 00:10:27,158
Unafanya kazi ya muda wapi?

155
00:10:27,182 --> 00:10:30,816
Katika duka la karibu na kituo cha treni.

156
00:10:30,839 --> 00:10:34,339
Unafanya kazi saa ngapi hadi saa ngapi?

157
00:10:34,362 --> 00:10:39,881
Kuanzia saa kumi na moja jioni hadi saa tatu usiku.

158
00:10:39,904 --> 00:10:42,737
Ni ngumu sana!

159
00:10:42,760 --> 00:10:47,227
Unafanya kazi mara ngapi kwa wiki?

160
00:10:47,250 --> 00:10:50,750
Mara tatu kwa wiki.

161
00:10:50,773 --> 00:10:54,485
Unapata pesa nyingi?

162
00:10:54,509 --> 00:10:58,776
Hapana, si nyingi sana.

163
00:10:58,799 --> 00:11:02,534
Lakini ni ya furaha.

164
00:11:02,557 --> 00:11:06,746
Unaongea na wateja kwa Kijapani?

165
00:11:06,769 --> 00:11:08,836
Ndiyo.

166
00:11:08,859 --> 00:11:11,725
Ndio, kila siku.

167
00:11:11,748 --> 00:11:15,048
Ni somo zuri sana.

168
00:11:15,071 --> 00:11:19,138
Ninataka pia kufanya kazi ya muda.

169
00:11:19,161 --> 00:11:24,548
Basi, nitaulize meneja wa duka langu?

170
00:11:24,572 --> 00:11:27,038
Kweli?

171
00:11:27,061 --> 00:11:29,660
Tafadhali.

172
00:11:29,684 --> 00:11:31,917
Ndiyo.

173
00:11:31,940 --> 00:11:35,486
Basi, sasa nitakuwa nikiondoka.

174
00:11:35,509 --> 00:11:38,009
Fanya bidii.

175
00:11:38,032 --> 00:11:40,499
Tutaonana kesho.

176
00:11:40,522 --> 00:11:43,422
Tutaonana kesho.

177
00:11:43,445 --> 00:11:46,383
Rudi salama.

178
00:11:46,406 --> 00:11:49,406
Mstari wa 7: Ununuzi na Maandalizi ya Chakula cha Jioni

179
00:11:49,406 --> 00:11:55,397
Leo tutapika nini kwa chakula cha jioni?

180
00:11:55,421 --> 00:12:01,214
Ninapenda kula nyama.

181
00:12:01,237 --> 00:12:07,471
Basi, twendeni kununua vyakula kwenye supamaketi.

182
00:12:07,494 --> 00:12:13,285
Tutakwenda supamaketi iliyo mbele ya kituo cha treni?

183
00:12:13,308 --> 00:12:20,941
Ndiyo, huko mboga zake ni rahisi.

184
00:12:20,964 --> 00:12:28,031
Ndani ya duka hapa ni baridi sana, sivyo?

185
00:12:28,055 --> 00:12:37,653
Ndiyo, kiyoyozi kinafanya kazi vizuri mno.

186
00:12:37,677 --> 00:12:41,667
Nyama iko wapi?

187
00:12:41,691 --> 00:12:50,524
Iko huko, karibu na samaki.

188
00:12:50,547 --> 00:12:57,532
Unapenda nyama ya nguruwe au ya ng'ombe?

189
00:12:57,555 --> 00:13:05,904
Napenda zote mbili, lakini leo tutatumia nyama ya nguruwe.

190
00:13:05,928 --> 00:13:14,161
Sawa. Nyama hii ya nguruwe inakuwaje?

191
00:13:14,184 --> 00:13:24,417
Shilingi mia tatu. Ni rahisi, basi tutanunue hiyo.

192
00:13:24,440 --> 00:13:29,632
Tutanunua mboga gani?

193
00:13:29,656 --> 00:13:36,289
Tutanunua kabichi na kitunguu.

194
00:13:36,312 --> 00:13:42,579
Pia ninahitaji mayai.

195
00:13:42,602 --> 00:13:51,270
Mayai bado yapo kwenye jokofu ya nyumbani.

196
00:13:51,293 --> 00:13:57,806
Aa, basi haya tu yanatosha.

197
00:13:57,830 --> 00:14:04,339
Ndiyo, twendeni kwenye kasiriba.

198
00:14:04,362 --> 00:14:12,396
Mimi nitatoa pesa.

199
00:14:12,419 --> 00:14:15,419
Mstari wa 8: Mazungumzo Wakati wa Chakula

200
00:14:15,419 --> 00:14:19,393
Chakula kimeandaliwa!

201
00:14:19,417 --> 00:14:23,983
Waa, harufu nzuri sana!

202
00:14:24,006 --> 00:14:30,513
Leo tuna nyama ya nguruwe na mboga zilizochomwa.

203
00:14:30,537 --> 00:14:33,670
Inaonekana kuwa tamu sana.

204
00:14:33,693 --> 00:14:36,165
Nakula.

205
00:14:36,188 --> 00:14:38,766
Nakula.

206
00:14:38,790 --> 00:14:42,256
Ladha yake inakuwaje?

207
00:14:42,279 --> 00:14:46,146
Nzuri sana!

208
00:14:46,169 --> 00:14:49,738
Ina uchungu kidogo.

209
00:14:49,762 --> 00:14:52,595
Samahani.

210
00:14:52,618 --> 00:14:57,285
Mimi napenda vyakula vyenye uchungu.

211
00:14:57,308 --> 00:15:00,226
Hakuna matata.

212
00:15:00,249 --> 00:15:04,149
Mimi pia napenda vyakula vyenye uchungu.

213
00:15:04,172 --> 00:15:07,715
Unataka chai?

214
00:15:07,739 --> 00:15:11,209
Ndiyo, tafadhali.

215
00:15:11,232 --> 00:15:15,466
Kazi ya muda ya leo ilikuwaje?

216
00:15:15,489 --> 00:15:20,756
Ilikuwa na shughuli nyingi, lakini nilifurahia.

217
00:15:20,780 --> 00:15:23,939
Hiyo ni nzuri.

218
00:15:23,963 --> 00:15:27,063
Umechoka?

219
00:15:27,086 --> 00:15:32,224
Ndiyo, miguu yangu inaniuma kidogo.

220
00:15:32,247 --> 00:15:37,349
Ingia bafuni na pumzika polepole.

221
00:15:37,372 --> 00:15:40,839
Ndiyo, nitakufanya hivyo.

222
00:15:40,862 --> 00:15:46,046
Chakula hiki ni tamu sana, kweli!

223
00:15:46,069 --> 00:15:49,136
Asante.

224
00:15:49,159 --> 00:15:52,533
Ungependa kula zaidi?

225
00:15:52,556 --> 00:15:57,089
Ndiyo, nipatie kidogo tafadhali.

226
00:15:57,112 --> 00:16:02,882
Kuna tele, kula yote usisite.

227
00:16:02,906 --> 00:16:08,246
Ndiyo, ni tamu sana, nitakula yote.

228
00:16:08,269 --> 00:16:11,269
Sehemu ya 9: Mazungumzo ya Kila Siku na Hiari

229
00:16:11,269 --> 00:16:15,369
Naweza kuwasha televisheni?

230
00:16:15,392 --> 00:16:18,950
Ndiyo, karibu.

231
00:16:18,974 --> 00:16:23,768
Kuna programu yoyote ya kuvutia?

232
00:16:23,791 --> 00:16:29,258
Anime yangu inapendeza inaanza sasa hivi.

233
00:16:29,282 --> 00:16:32,191
Ni anime ya aina gani?

234
00:16:32,214 --> 00:16:37,914
Ni anime kuhusu wanafunzi wa sekondari wanaocheza michezo.

235
00:16:37,937 --> 00:16:42,614
Hmm, inaonekana nzuri sana!

236
00:16:42,637 --> 00:16:46,137
Ninapenda kuiongea pia.

237
00:16:46,160 --> 00:16:50,193
Ina umaarufu sana, wewe utaipenda!

238
00:16:50,216 --> 00:16:54,283
Wimbo huu ni mzuri sana!

239
00:16:54,306 --> 00:16:57,373
Ni wimbo wa nani?

240
00:16:57,396 --> 00:17:01,989
Ni wimbo wa bendi maarufu.

241
00:17:02,012 --> 00:17:04,845
Unaisikiliza mara kwa mara?

242
00:17:04,868 --> 00:17:11,168
Ndiyo, nasikiliza kwa mtandao wakati mwingine.

243
00:17:11,191 --> 00:17:15,334
Mimi nasikiliza kila siku.

244
00:17:15,358 --> 00:17:20,425
Kuna wahusika wengi wa anime hapa, kweli!

245
00:17:20,448 --> 00:17:27,481
Ndiyo, ninampenda yule mvulana mwenye nywele ndefu.

246
00:17:27,504 --> 00:17:30,538
Anapendeza sana!

247
00:17:30,561 --> 00:17:34,194
Je, ana nguvu?

248
00:17:34,217 --> 00:17:40,057
Ndiyo, ni mwenye nguvu zaidi na mpole pia.

249
00:17:40,080 --> 00:17:43,947
Ninahisi hamu ya kusikia hadithi yake.

250
00:17:43,970 --> 00:17:50,070
Inatangazwa kila Ijumaa jioni.

251
00:17:50,093 --> 00:17:54,526
Basi, tutaiongea pamoja wiki ijayo.

252
00:17:54,549 --> 00:17:58,095
Sawa, hivi ndivyo tutakavyofanya.

253
00:17:58,118 --> 00:18:02,356
Tutakiione pamoja na vitabu vya chakula?

254
00:18:02,379 --> 00:18:05,716
Mimi nitakuletea.

255
00:18:05,740 --> 00:18:08,740
Sehemu ya 10: Mazungumzo Kuhusu Likizo na Kazi za Muda

256
00:18:08,740 --> 00:18:13,730
Saa zimekuwa kumi na nusu usiku, kweli!

257
00:18:13,753 --> 00:18:18,427
Ndiyo, ni wakati wa kulala.

258
00:18:18,451 --> 00:18:22,685
Kesho utasimu saa ngapi?

259
00:18:22,708 --> 00:18:28,275
Kesho ni likizo, nitasimu polepole.

260
00:18:28,298 --> 00:18:31,238
Sawa, hiyo ni wazo zuri.

261
00:18:31,261 --> 00:18:35,830
Mimi kesho nina kazi ya muda.

262
00:18:35,854 --> 00:18:37,891
Aa,

263
00:18:37,914 --> 00:18:41,687
Je, una kazi ya muda hata Jumapili?

264
00:18:41,711 --> 00:18:46,211
Ndiyo, saa tatu asubuhi.

265
00:18:46,234 --> 00:18:49,615
Hiyo ni ngumu sana!

266
00:18:49,639 --> 00:18:53,226
Utaisha saa ngapi?

267
00:18:53,249 --> 00:18:57,034
Nitaisha saa nane mchana.

268
00:18:57,058 --> 00:19:02,091
Basi, utakua na muda mchana.

269
00:19:02,114 --> 00:19:08,181
Ndiyo. Mchana nitapanga kusafisha na kufua nguo.

270
00:19:08,203 --> 00:19:12,637
Nitakusaidia kusafisha chumba.

271
00:19:12,660 --> 00:19:15,371
Kweli?

272
00:19:15,395 --> 00:19:18,153
Asante.

273
00:19:18,176 --> 00:19:23,743
Asante, wewe huwapikia chakula daima.

274
00:19:23,766 --> 00:19:26,315
Asante sana.

275
00:19:26,338 --> 00:19:31,910
Basi, tutasafisha pamoja kuanzia saa tisa mchana kesho.

276
00:19:31,933 --> 00:19:34,666
Sawa.

277
00:19:34,689 --> 00:19:39,356
Umeangalia habari za hali ya hewa ya leo?

278
00:19:39,379 --> 00:19:45,515
Ndiyo, walisema kesho itakuwa na hali nzuri ya hewa.

279
00:19:45,538 --> 00:19:49,679
Nguo zitakauka vizuri, basi!

280
00:19:49,703 --> 00:19:52,136
Ndiyo, kweli.

281
00:19:52,159 --> 00:19:55,992
Basi, nitazima taa.

282
00:19:56,015 --> 00:19:59,954
Sawa. Lala salama.

283
00:19:59,978 --> 00:20:02,617
Lala salama.

284
00:20:02,640 --> 00:20:05,340
Tutaonana kesho.